1. Core Computing & Display
brain: Raspberry Pi 5 (8GB or 4GB RAM recommended).
Cooling: Raspberry Pi Active Cooler (Official SC1148).
Storage: 64GB (or higher) Class 10 microSD Card.
Display: Waveshare 7-inch HDMI LCD (Resistive Touch, XPT2046 Controller, 1024x600 resolution).

2. Input & Control
Keyboard: COOLCOLD Mini Wireless Keyboard (with track pad).

3. Chassis & Structure (Custom)
Screen Frame: 3D Printed Custom Case (169mm x 129mm).
Keyboard Base: 3D Printed Custom Case (146.8mm x 97.5mm).
Fasteners: * 4x M2.5 Screws (for mounting the Pi to the frame).
4x M3 Screws/Bolts (for the outer corner "ear" mounts).

4. Software Stack
OS: Raspberry Pi OS (64-bit).
